                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-42-off209 t17850914-42-cd210"></join> last, one linen handkerchief, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850914-42-victim527" type="victimName">
                     John 
